      <data key="edge_doi">10.1186/s13568-022-01418-6</data>
      <data key="edge_evidence">MKs are subject to feedback inhibition by lycopene biosynthesis intermediates, such as geranyldiphosphate (GPP), farnesyldiphosphate (FPP), and geranylgeranyldiphosphate (GGPP)</data>
