      <data key="edge_confidence">MEDIUM</data>
      <data key="edge_mechanism">Dxs consumes G3P + pyruvate into DXP; strong Dxs OE depletes G3P. Wang 2009 MAGE finds balanced (not maximal) RBS tuning for dxs/idi/ispD/ispE/ispF gives the optimum, implying a non-monotonic dose-response.</data>
      <data key="edge_doi">10.1038/nature08187</data>
      <data key="edge_evidence">applied MAGE to optimize the 1-deoxy-D-xylulose-5-phosphate biosynthesis pathway in E. coli to overproduce lycopene... isolated variants with more than fivefold increase in lycopene production within 3 days</data>
    </edge>
