      <data key="edge_doi">10.3390/molecules25143136</data>
      <data key="edge_evidence">highest lycopene yield (22 mg/L) was reached with the arabinose-inducible promoter on a medium-copy plasmid pBAD24 in the E. coli XL1-Blue strain</data>
